</p>
<p>publication/266820089_Human_rights_violations_in_the_Maquiladora_Industry. 
</p>
<p> 19 Robert E. Scott, &#8220;The high price of &#8216;free&#8217; trade: NAFTA&#8217;s failure has cost the United States jobs 
</p>
